flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 48: Vendor Dashboard Frontend Architecture Flow

  Dashboard[Vendor Dashboard Shell]
  KPI[KPI and forecast widgets]
  Opp[Opportunity panel]
  Catalog[Product and stock management]
  Sahayak[Sahayak panel]
  Live[Live/Reels controls]
  POS[POS entry]

  ReadAPI[Forecast/opportunity read APIs]
  ActionIntent[Coupon/pricing/inventory action intent]
  Confirm{User confirms state-changing action?}
  ActionAPI[Execute mutation APIs]
  Abort[Abort mutation]
  ActionFail[Mutation failed]
  Recover[Show rollback-safe UI and retry option]
  Refresh[Refresh dashboard state]

  Dashboard --> KPI --> ReadAPI
  Dashboard --> Opp --> ReadAPI
  Dashboard --> Catalog --> ActionIntent
  Dashboard --> Sahayak --> ActionIntent
  Dashboard --> Live
  Dashboard --> POS

  ActionIntent --> Confirm
  Confirm -- Yes --> ActionAPI
  Confirm -- No --> Abort

  ActionAPI -->|Success| Refresh
  ActionAPI -->|Failure| ActionFail --> Recover --> ActionIntent
